headline: Ethisphere Names Henry Schein as One of the 2025 World's Most Ethical Companies® for 14th Consecutive Year
summary: MELVILLE, N.Y., March 11, 2025--Henry Schein, Inc. (Nasdaq: HSIC), the world’s largest provider of health care solutions to office-based dental and medical practitioners, has received the 2025 World’s Most Ethical Companies® recognition by Ethisphere, a global leader in defining and advancing the standards of ethical business practices.
